  Artifact: silero-vad-unified-256ms-v6.2.1.mlmodelc
  License: MIT (HuggingFace cardData.license = mit)

The FluidInference conversion is distributed under the MIT license. MIT
requires preserving the notice; this record (repo id, revision, license) is
