────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
3. Whisper models (audio::whisper)

audio::whisper is a Rust port of Argmax's WhisperKit (MIT,
https://github.com/argmaxinc/WhisperKit). It loads the compiled WhisperKit
CoreML bundles from argmaxinc/whisperkit-coreml
(https://huggingface.co/argmaxinc/whisperkit-coreml); the underlying Whisper
model is OpenAI's (https://github.com/openai/whisper, MIT). Preserve the
WhisperKit and OpenAI Whisper notices when redistributing a binary that
includes these weights.

